Package: HCCMultiOmics
Title: An Integrative AutoML Framework for Multiscale Biological Discovery
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Zhuo Chen [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Zhuo Chen <cz050529@163.com>
Authors@R: 
    person("Zhuo", "Chen", email = "cz050529@163.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive and automated workflow designed to translate multi-omics 
    data into actionable biological mechanisms. The framework integrates an ensemble 
    machine learning engine (LASSO, RSF, XGBoost) for robust prognostic biomarker 
    discovery, coupled with an adaptive single-cell mechanistic decoding module to 
    profile intracellular trajectories, stemness, and intercellular communication.
